1362
01:13:20,227 --> 01:13:22,267
No me resulta fácil.

1363
01:13:23,690 --> 01:13:24,721
¿Sí?

1364
01:13:31,824 --> 01:13:34,030
Mira, yo sigo trabajando

1365
01:13:34,827 --> 01:13:38,196
